videos.headline: Akers punches it in for FSU score
videos.description: Cam Akers takes the handoff and shoves through the pile at the goal line to put Florida State on the board in the first quarter vs. Louisville.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Akers punches it in for FSU score) 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Akers scores his second TD of the 1st quarter
videos.description: Cam Akers rushes 4 yards to the end zone to score his second touchdown and Florida State's third to give the Seminoles a solid lead heading into the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Akers scores his second TD of the 1st quarter) 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Atwell's toe-tapping touchdown puts Louisville on the board
videos.description: Malik Cunningham finds Tutu Atwell in the corner of the end zone for a 9-yard touchdown vs. Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Atwell's toe-tapping touchdown puts Louisville on the board) 2019/9/21

videos.headline: Fitzpatrick's impressive catch and 74-yard TD gives Louisville lead
videos.description: Malik Cunningham lets it sail to Dez Fitzpatrick for a 74-yard touchdown that gives Louisville their first lead of the game vs. Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fitzpatrick's impressive catch and 74-yard TD gives Louisville lead) 2019/9/21
